name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Morty, we just got him back!

name: Agent
line: Did he die?

name: Rick
line: He was captured by the Federation and we were going to rescue him.

name: Agent
line: Jerry, tell your parents the first law of Thermodynamics.

name: Rick
line: "The increment in the internal energy of a system is equal to the increment of heat supplied to the system." Wow! Thermodynamically active, Jerry!

name: Agent
line: Wow! Therapists, we're growing.

name: Rick
line: Weird breed.

name: Agent
line: Yeah, I'm pretty sure that's a dad thing.

name: Rick
line: That's not a dad move, Jerry.

name: Agent
line: Look, I know I-I know you're probably being obstinate, but look at how hot he is. You know, even his dad is like, I mean, you know, I could be his science teacher.

name: Rick
line: Dad, what are you doing with my stuff?

name: Agent
line: I'm inventing a new super weapon for when I'm not allowed to shoot robots.

name: Rick
line: Then you should make sure to shoot the robots first.

name: Agent
line: What? Why not?

name: Rick
line: You should know that by now, Rick.

name: Agent
line: I-I don't want to shoot any of those!

name: Rick
line: That is absolutely ridiculous!

name: Agent
line: You're putting too much pressure on yourself!

name: Rick
line: Why not shoot the bull?

name: Agent
line: It's a dog!
